data.description: Beautifully renovated three bedroom, 2.5 bath home nestled in a quiet neighborhood at the end of a dead end street. 10' ceilings on the main floor, master bedroom with walk-in closet, beautiful laminate and tile flooring throughout, granite countertops in kitchen, guest bathroom on main floor, and living rooms both upstairs and downstairs.  Half bathroom and built in cabinets with shelves in basement. Exterior of the home was just repainted.  New carpet with memory foam pad in all bedrooms and downstairs living room.  Furnace and air conditioning replaced three years ago and are still under warranty.  Water heater replaced last year.  Generous storage space in cellar with a separate laundry room area. Back and front yard are fully fenced offering great privacy.  Beautifully landscaped yard with large12x12 pergola on back patio for entertaining and lounging during warm summer nights.
